{"repo": {"timestamp": 1624107359000, "version": 21, "name": "Iod\u00e9OS apps", "icon": "fdroid-icon.png", "address": "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/iodeOS/fdroid/master/fdroid/repo", "description": "This is a repository of iod\u00e9OS apps to be used with F-Droid. ", "mirrors": ["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/iodeOS/fdroid/master/fdroid/repo"]}, "requests": {"install": [], "uninstall": []}, "apps": [{"authorName": "iod\u00e9 Team (forked from FDroid Team)", "categories": ["Apps for iod\u00e9OS"], "suggestedVersionCode": "1013010", "description": "<p>We forked FDroid in order to give the iod\u00e9 repository a higher priority than prebuilt repos, and to reset the repos database if needed (particularly, for already running instances of the iod\u00e9OS ROM).</p>", "license": "GPL-3.0-or-later", "name": "F-Droid", "sourceCode": "https://gitlab.com/iode/os/apps/fdroid", "summary": "iod\u00e9OS version of F-Droid", "added": 1608561236000, "icon": "org.fdroid.fdroid.1013010.png", "packageName": "org.fdroid.fdroid", "lastUpdated": 1622806440000}, {"authorName": "iod\u00e9 Team (forked from official microG)", "categories": ["Apps for iod\u00e9OS"], "suggestedVersionCode": "2", "license": "Apache-2.0", "name": "FakeStore", "sourceCode": "https://gitlab.com/iode/os/apps/fakestore", "summary": "iod\u00e9OS version of microG FakeStore", "added": 1608561236000, "icon": "com.android.vending.2.png", "packageName": "com.android.vending", "lastUpdated": 1608561236000}, {"authorName": "iod\u00e9 Team", "categories": ["Apps for iod\u00e9OS"], "suggestedVersionCode": "2", "license": "Unknown", "name": "iod\u00e9", "summary": "User interface for the iod\u00e9 {ad/malware/data leak}-blocker", "added": 1608561244000, "icon": "com.iode.app.2.png", "packageName": "com.iode.app", "lastUpdated": 1608561244000}, {"authorName": "iod\u00e9 Team (forked from official Firefox)", "categories": ["Apps for iod\u00e9OS"], "suggestedVersionCode": "11", "description": "<p>This Firefox fork has the following features:</p><ul><li> Telemetry disabled and its corresponding code partially removed (trackers Adjust, Google AdMob, LeanPlum).</li><li> Alternative search engine: if Qwant is natively available (official plugin) it is chosen by default, else DuckDuckGo official plugin, else as a fallaback a custom Qwant plugin which does not have search suggestions.</li><li> Several search engines added (with no search suggestions): Ecosia, Qwant light, Startpage, and several Searx instances.</li><li> Qwant replaces Google in the hard-coded top sites.</li><li> Several menu entries removed: telemetry, USB debugging, Vote on Google Play.</li></ul>", "license": "MPL-2.0", "name": "Iod\u00e9 Browser", "sourceCode": "https://gitlab.com/iode/os/apps/firefox", "summary": "Browser based on Mozilla Firefox, with alternative default search engine and no telemetry.", "added": 1615128466000, "icon": "com.iode.firefox.11.png", "packageName": "com.iode.firefox", "lastUpdated": 1622806445000}, {"authorName": "iod\u00e9 Team (forked from official LineageOS Jelly)", "categories": ["Apps for iod\u00e9OS"], "suggestedVersionCode": "4", "description": "<p>Jelly is the official browser of LineageOS. We tweaked it to set Qwant as the default search engine and suggestions provider, and added several alternative search engines (Ecosia, Startpage, several Searx instances).</p>", "license": "Apache-2.0", "name": "Jelly", "sourceCode": "https://gitlab.com/iode/os/apps/jelly", "summary": "iod\u00e9OS version of LineageOS browser, with alternative search engines", "added": 1608561254000, "packageName": "com.iode.jelly", "lastUpdated": 1622806110000}, {"authorName": "iod\u00e9 Team (forked from official microG)", "categories": ["Apps for iod\u00e9OS"], "suggestedVersionCode": "211515048", "license": "Apache-2.0", "name": "microG Services Core", "sourceCode": "https://gitlab.com/iode/os/apps/gmscore", "added": 1615128462000, "icon": "com.google.android.gms.211515048.png", "packageName": "com.googl